<h2 id="home-office-press-office">Home Office press office</h2>

<p>Journalists with enquiries can call the Home Office news desk on 020 7035 3535.</p>

<p>The desk operates from 7am to 8pm, Monday to Friday.</p>

<p>If you are not a member of the media, please use the Home Office public enquiries line: 020 7035 4848.</p>

<p>Press office out of hours number: 07623 514 628. Only urgent media calls will be attended to.</p>

